{"tid":751293,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人學資處漏報","createTime":"2018-07-21T17:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T02:22:10.000Z","uid":165232,"like":3,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ac002a60d7c7fe4dfa400d465421d94721b09a3e","tid":751293,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"岩岩收到封警告信<br />\n話我漏報父母銀行戶口同報錯收入<br />\n<br />\n我即刻上返網睇<br />\n原來我申請表個到收入寫左一個月而唔係全年<br />\n仲有兩個銀行戶口打漏左<br />\n<br />\n但係收入證明同個兩個銀行戶口既資料我都有交齊<br />\n<br />\n純粹係申請表寫錯<br />\n<br />\n想問咁樣批既機會大唔大？<br />\n<br />\n星期日又打唔到電話問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇佢個名都似係老姑婆嚟<br />\n寫錯申請表又唔係冇交資料就問都唔問出警告信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb0342cc160cf9cfe9df3131301972087fe03c9","tid":751293,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"批既機會唔大<br />\n試過<br />\n拿拿聲補交啦屌"},{"pid":"555ddfffd12c03b8a48bb4e3dd281bd7ec6c1d80","tid":751293,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cb0342cc160cf9cfe9df3131301972087fe03c9","tid":751293,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"批既機會唔大<br />\n試過<br />\n拿拿聲補交啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:03:18.000Z","msg":"我資料一早交左<br />\n<br />\n係申請表寫錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff410275afdc2b8092596ad0fe3f99f8272e98a2","tid":751293,"uid":137485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"點解睇名都估到係老姑婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69af6052bc8bca45f5b36d49e84cd818fcd01f97","tid":751293,"uid":165232,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ff410275afdc2b8092596ad0fe3f99f8272e98a2","tid":751293,"uid":137485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:04:34.